Package eu.fbk.st.cryptoac.tuple

Class RoleTuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.fbk.st.cryptoac.tuple.CryptoACTuple
      • eu.fbk.st.cryptoac.tuple.RoleTuple
  • public class RoleTuple
extends CryptoACTuple
    This tuple binds a user to a role, thus gives access to the role's keys. The associated element is the user, the tuple-specific element is the role

        public RoleTuple​(java.lang.String associatedElement,
                 java.lang.String associatedRole,
                 byte[] encryptedPublicRoleKey,
                 byte[] encryptedPrivateRoleKey,
                 int roleVersionNumber)
        Constructor. Initialize the variables of the class
        Parameters:
        associatedElement - the associated element
        associatedRole - the associated role
        encryptedPublicRoleKey - the public PKI key of the role, encrypted with the public key of the user
        encryptedPrivateRoleKey - the private PKI key of the role, encrypted with the public key of the user
        roleVersionNumber - the related role version number. A negative or zero value will be set to 1 by default
